data.description:
Welcome to Estrella Mountain Ranch, one of Goodyear's most sought after communities! This stunning 5 bedroom, 4 bathroom home is the epitome of luxury and style. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the attention to detail and high-end finishes that set this home apart. The downstairs features wood-look tile flooring, 9+ foot ceilings, and plenty of natural light in every room. Each of the bedrooms boasts ceiling fans and blackout shades for optimal privacy and comfort. Entertain in style in the spacious kitchen with stainless steel Whirlpool appliances, a large island, quartz countertops, tile backsplash, and a butler's pantry. The primary suite is a true oasis, complete with a large walk-in closet, double sinks, and a massive walk-in shower. The best part about this home is its unbeatable location! There are two community clubhouses with pools, a golf course, splash pad, community garden, lake, hiking and biking trails, and restaurants just minutes away from your door, plus weekly/monthly events that really bring this neighborhood to life.

The backyard is a blank canvas for you to create your dream outdoor living space. Whether you want to host summer barbecues or cozy up around a fire pit in the winter, the gas stub is ready for you to make it your own.

Make this charming house your new home today!
